# (To-Do List)

#### Date 12/04/2024

#### By *Mungai John*

## Description
This is a simple web application for managing daily tasks.On the home page it show 3 common tasks of a house manager which are deletable. The users can add,delete and mark tasks as completed.It also support dark mode and light mode for better experience.

## Features
Add tasks: Users can enter new tasks in the input box and click the "Add" button to add them to the list.
Delete tasks: Users can delete tasks by clicking on the delete button (represented by a trash can icon) next to each task.
Mark tasks as completed: Users can mark tasks as completed by clicking on the task itself. Completed tasks will be distinguished from incomplete tasks by strikethrough.
Dark mode: User can toggle between light and dark modes by clicking on the "Toggle Mode"

## Usage
Adding Tasks: Enter your task in the input box and click the "Add" button to add it to the list.
Deleting Tasks: Click the delete button next to a task to remove it from the list.
Marking Tasks as Completed: Click on a task to mark it as completed. Click again to undo the completion.
Toggle Mode:click the "Toggle Mode" button to switch between light and dark mode.

